1: # Redesign Walkthrough: Apple-Style Redesign (Reverts & Fixes)
2: 
3: We have successfully reverted the edge-to-edge gradients and TopAppBar modifications from the previous run as requested, while fixing the theme settings bug in all of our custom glassmorphic components.
4: 
5: ## Reverts Executed
